  | language = 
  | publisher = New York Times
  | date = 25 November, 1928
  | url = }}</ref> In January, 1932 the Home completed a $92,000 expansion which provided room for a total of 41 residents.<ref>{{cite news 
  | last = 
  | first = 
  | coauthors = 
  | title = Victoria Home Unit Nearing Completion
  | work = 
